# market-tickers

A lightweight Python library to map human-friendly stock and index names  
to Yahoo Finance–compatible tickers.

## Features
- Indian & US stocks
- Indian, US & global indices
- Fuzzy name matching
- Stock → default index mapping
- CSV-based, easy to maintain

## Installation (after pip release)
```bash
pip install market-tickers
